      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks these are good. but some of my regulars are actually kinda vocal about not liking the whole \"DEI\" thing... some think it's just performative or political. can u give me one version that's a bit more \"neutral\" or less \"activist\" sounding? like focus more on the community aspect without using the actual words DEI or equity?",
