      "role": "user",
      "content": "those are nice and safe, but i'm still a bit worried. i had one customer tell me that by even implying we care about \"backgrounds,\" we're basically taking a political side against people who believe in tradition. do u think it's actually possible to be truly neutral on this, or is it better to just accept that being a \"welcoming\" business is inherently a political stance nowadays?",
